{"tid":1568614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發 懷疑淘大廢老尾隧手足一齊搭巴士走報串 便衣警埋伏拉人","createTime":"2019-09-14T10:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T11:46:01.000Z","uid":167548,"like":129,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"245da05e7ab9877c0524032478c246d0d15cdcaa","tid":1568614,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:30:34.000Z","msg":"【讀者報料】今天下午，兩名乘坐往來淘大及樂華邨的九巴 2A 號巴的乘客，在樂華下車時被兩名疑似休班警員制服，疑似休班警展示伸縮警棍防御，但並無揮動，青年掙扎呼喊叫救命，巴士司機上前問身穿間條衫的男子有沒有警員委任證，男子稱要投訴司機。片段可見該名警員有配槍。<br />\n讀者質疑，樂華邨當時無任何示威或人群眾集，那兩人究竟是當值便衣警還是休班警，為何如此執法？<br />\n《立場新聞》正向警察公共關係科求證有關行動的來龍去脈。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/?__tn__=kC-R0.g&amp;eid=ARBLX3J7Srx-UowE1BR8K-uWh7kGWkAb1UN7lHgj7YGSmX3O_zQ_EDlBwosPn7CDXctn7khkiI1UTCM4&amp;hc_ref=ARTcCwaBuCr7A30gCUv8mmmSiA1zrEQImYQZu4McrbZ55_ei22SeJDaXc9oHO7EC3VY&amp;fref=nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2F%3F__tn__%3DkC-R0.g%26eid%3DARBLX3J7Srx-UowE1BR8K-uWh7kGWkAb1UN7lHgj7YGSmX3O_zQ_EDlBwosPn7CDXctn7khkiI1UTCM4%26hc_ref%3DARTcCwaBuCr7A30gCUv8mmmSiA1zrEQImYQZu4McrbZ55_ei22SeJDaXc9oHO7EC3VY%26fref%3Dnf&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=ade47457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/?__tn__=kC-R0.g&amp;eid=ARBLX3J7Srx-UowE1BR8K-uWh7kGWkAb1UN7lHgj7YGSmX3O_zQ_EDlBwosPn7CDXctn7khkiI1UTCM4&amp;hc_ref=ARTcCwaBuCr7A30gCUv8mmmSiA1zrEQImYQZu4McrbZ55_ei22SeJDaXc9oHO7EC3VY&amp;fref=nf</a><br />\n<br />\n裏面有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1bde3bdb694cf069b409fcc5924f5286a7ca229","tid":1568614,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f018045b6f577d3addacb59f01d10a60680bb94c","tid":1568614,"uid":117906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"